libpydhcpserver (2.0.0~beta) unstable; urgency=low

  * Finally refactored DHCPPacket.
  
  * Options can now be set with Python data-types, rather than lists of bytes.
  
  * Internal memory-management for packst should now be tighter and faster.

 -- Neil Tallim <flan@uguu.ca>  Fri, 27 Sep 2013 07:00:00 -0600

libpydhcpserver (1.4.0~beta) unstable; urgency=low

  * Refactoring and relocation of code, cleaning up dhcp a little and
    concentrating all functions in conversion.

 -- Neil Tallim <flan@uguu.ca>  Wed, 25 Sep 2013 07:00:00 -0600

libpydhcpserver (1.3.0~beta) unstable; urgency=low

  * Huge rewrite to the networking logic, allowing for layer 2 packets and
    moving all server-related logic into libpydhcpserver
    - Support for qtags (vlans) now provided for raw packets

  * Renamed modules and made what should be the last significant API change.

 -- Neil Tallim <flan@uguu.ca>  Fri, 13 Sep 2013 07:00:00 -0600

